<i>noun</i>: 동거 [동거] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>동거 [동거]</dt><br>
<dd>1. living together</dd><br>
<dd>같은 집이나 같은 방에서 함께 삶.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of living together in the same house or room.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cohabitation</dd><br>
<dd>결혼하지 않은 남녀가 부부처럼 한집에서 같이 삶.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of living together as husband and wife without getting married.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>